Segmentation Data This Excel document is focused on products and segments, it contains limited information on facilities, and is best used in conjunction with this report. Each product will appear multiple times within this document, one time for each facility that produced it, and one time for each segment that it falls into. By using the Excel filter functions of each column you can refine the data you are looking at to see which products are in each segment, products that are produced by a single facility, and what products facilities are producing. This report acts as a supplement to this document, presenting information from other sets of data to enable product related decision making.
